{"submission_id":"sub_8cc4aec3106d5a50","run_id":"2026-06-22T19-23-00-300Z_223560-4fc13728_ingest_meeting-doc-64096","submitted_at":"2026-06-22T19:28:53.477Z","tool_args_sha256":"sha256:8cc4aec3106d5a506cfe8e2d6b900b95e8254fca59573ab5ae834cccda92c915","schema_version":2,"tool_args":{"source_id":"meeting_doc_64096","observation_kind":"claim","local_observation_id":"claim_charter_revisions_purpose","label":"Charter revisions consolidate C&D procurement under CPOC","raw_text":"To seek Board approval of proposed revisions to the MTA Committee Charters for Capital Program Oversight (\"CPOC\"), New York City Transit/MTA Bus, Metro-North Railroad, Long Island Rail Road and Bridges and Tunnels. These proposed revisions will create increased efficiency and minimize redundancies by having all MTA Construction and Development (\"C&D\") procurement contracts, that require Board approval, be approved by CPOC instead of separately by each operating committee.","payload":{"claim_text":"Proposed revisions to MTA Committee Charters will create increased efficiency and minimize redundancies by having all MTA Construction and Development procurement contracts that require Board approval be approved by CPOC instead of separately by each operating committee.","description":"Revisions to CPOC, NYCT/MTA Bus, Metro-North, LIRR, and Bridges and Tunnels committee charters to consolidate C&D procurement approval under CPOC","change_type":"consolidation","change_type_normalized":{"raw_text":"consolidation","normalized_value":"consolidation"}},"evidence_refs":[{"source_id":"meeting_doc_64096","evidence_id":"meeting_doc_64096#p069_c0008","source_path":"raw/sources/meeting_doc_64096/blocks.jsonl","page_number":69,"block_id":"p069_c0008","text_sha256":"sha256:eaf155d16f9364235e149f88f498de3284c12e3eac727adc954651b1f74188af","text_source":"raw_text","source_quote":"To seek Board approval of proposed revisions to the MTA Committee Charters for Capital Program Oversight (\"CPOC\"), New York City Transit/MTA Bus, Metro-North Railroad, Long Island Rail Road and Bridges and Tunnels. These proposed revisions will create increased efficiency and minimize redundancies by having all MTA Construction and Development (\"C&D\") procurement contracts, that require Board approval, be approved by CPOC instead of separately by each operating committee."},{"source_id":"meeting_doc_64096","evidence_id":"meeting_doc_64096#p069_c0011","source_path":"raw/sources/meeting_doc_64096/blocks.jsonl","page_number":69,"block_id":"p069_c0011","text_sha256":"sha256:078d768f68df03e515faa6c5f9970000b0e0b8ead0e9ec5d231787bf8ec561b7","text_source":"raw_text","source_quote":"The proposed revisions to the Charters: (1) eliminate language in the operating committee's charter that refer to monitoring capital projects; (2) limits the committee's responsibility to non-capital contracts; and (3) removes oversight of C&D. These responsibilities will be assumed by CPOC."}]},"validation":{"state":"rejected","issues":["evidence_refs[0].source_quote must be 280 characters or fewer","evidence_refs[1].source_quote must be 280 characters or fewer"]}}
